---
import BaseLayout from '@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
const updated = new Date('2024-01-01');
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Privacy Policy | The Data Governor"
  description="Privacy policy for thedatagovernor.com — how we collect, use, and protect your information."
  canonicalPath="/privacy-policy/"
>
  <div class="page-wrap">
    <div class="page-header">
      <a href="/" class="label" style="font-size:0.65rem; letter-spacing:0.14em;">The Data Governor</a>
      <h1 class="page-title">Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="page-updated">Last updated: {updated.toLocaleDateString('en-US', { year: 'numeric', month: 'long', day: 'numeric' })}</p>
    </div>
    <div class="article-rule" aria-hidden="true"></div>

    <div class="page-body prose">
      <p>
        Your privacy is important to us. This Privacy Policy explains how The Data Governor
        ("we," "us," or "our") collects, uses, and protects information when you visit
        <strong>thedatagovernor.com</strong>.
      </p>

      <h2>Information We Collect</h2>
      <p>
        We collect information you voluntarily provide (such as when contacting us via email) and
        information collected automatically when you visit our site, including:
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li>Log data (IP address, browser type, pages visited, referring URL)</li>
        <li>Cookies and similar tracking technologies</li>
        <li>Device information (screen size, operating system)</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>How We Use Your Information</h2>
      <p>We use collected information to:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Analyze site traffic and improve content</li>
        <li>Respond to inquiries and support requests</li>
        <li>Serve relevant advertisements (via Google AdSense)</li>
        <li>Comply with legal obligations</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Google AdSense & Advertising</h2>
      <p>
        This site uses Google AdSense, which uses cookies to serve ads based on your prior visits to this
        and other websites. Google's use of advertising cookies enables it and its partners to serve ads
        to you based on your visit to this site and/or other sites on the internet.
      </p>
      <p>
        You may opt out of personalized advertising by visiting
        <a href="https://www.google.com/settings/ads" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Google Ads Settings</a>
        or <a href="https://optout.aboutads.info/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">aboutads.info</a>.
      </p>

      <h2>Affiliate Links</h2>
      <p>
        Some links on this site are affiliate links. If you click and make a purchase, we may receive a
        commission at no additional cost to you. See our <a href="/affiliate-disclosure/">Affiliate Disclosure</a>
        for full details.
      </p>

      <h2>Cookies</h2>
      <p>
        We use cookies for analytics and advertising purposes. You can disable cookies in your browser
        settings, though this may affect site functionality.
      </p>

      <h2>Third-Party Services</h2>
      <p>We may use the following third-party services, each with their own privacy policies:</p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Google Analytics</strong> — site traffic analysis</li>
        <li><strong>Google AdSense</strong> — advertising</li>
        <li><strong>YouTube</strong> — embedded video content</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Data Retention</h2>
      <p>
        We retain personal data only as long as necessary to provide our services or comply with legal
        requirements. Server logs are typically retained for 30–90 days.
      </p>

      <h2>Your Rights</h2>
      <p>
        Depending on your jurisdiction (EU/EEA, California, etc.), you may have rights to access,
        correct, delete, or restrict processing of your personal data. Contact us at
        <a href="mailto:thedatagovernor@gmail.com">thedatagovernor@gmail.com</a> to exercise these rights.
      </p>

      <h2>Children's Privacy</h2>
      <p>
        This site is not directed at children under 13. We do not knowingly collect personal information
        from children under 13.
      </p>

      <h2>Changes to This Policy</h2>
      <p>
        We may update this policy periodically. The updated date at the top of this page reflects the
        most recent revision. Continued use of the site after changes constitutes acceptance.
      </p>

      <h2>Contact</h2>
      <p>
        Questions about this privacy policy? Email us at
        <a href="mailto:thedatagovernor@gmail.com">thedatagovernor@gmail.com</a>.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .page-header {
    padding: 2.5rem 0 1.5rem;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.4rem;
  }

  .page-title {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3rem);
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--ink);
    line-height: 1.05;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .page-updated {
    font-family: var(--font-ui);
    font-size: 0.68rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--ink-faint);
    margin: 0;
  }

  .article-rule {
    height: 3px;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--red) 0%, var(--gold) 50%, transparent 100%);
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
  }

  .page-body {
    max-width: 740px;
    padding-bottom: 4rem;
  }

  .prose {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 1.08rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: var(--ink);
  }
  .prose p { margin-bottom: 1.4rem; }
  .prose h2 {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--ink);
    margin: 2rem 0 0.6rem;
    padding-top: 1.25rem;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--rule);
  }
  .prose ul { padding-left: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 1.4rem; }
  .prose li { margin-bottom: 0.4rem; padding-left: 0.25rem; }
  .prose li::marker { color: var(--red); }
  .prose a { color: var(--red); text-decoration: underline; text-underline-offset: 3px; }
  .prose a:hover { color: var(--red-dark); }
  .prose strong { font-weight: 700; }
</style>
